    public abstract class AbstractAlgorithmParametersSpiImpl<P extends java.security.spec.AlgorithmParameterSpec>
extends java.security.AlgorithmParametersSpi
    A base class for classes which implement AlgorithmParametersSpi that encode parameters using ASN.1.
